item.description:
We will meet at Martha's Exchange at 4:30 to hand out literature and greet the peopl on the Holiday Stroll.
At that time, we will decide where to stand for handing out constitutions and literature.

There will be entertainment and food etc. available at many of downtown Nashua's restaurants. There will be bands playing and people out for a good time. Let's make it a good night for Ron Paul by introducing him to more voters.

I apologize for the short notice. Please RSVP and plan to be there with us.
item.name: Nashua Holiday Stroll - visibility and outreach
